videos.description: Alterique Gilbert gets by a defender with a hesitation then finishes around the rim with a nice layup.
videos.headline: Gilbert finishes with a scoop lay-in after blowing by a defender

videos.description: Christian Vital comes up with a steal and throws down a fast-break dunk.
videos.headline: Vital hammers home fast-break jam

videos.description: Tre Scott catches an offensive rebound and goes back up for a buzzer-beating putback for Cincinnati.
videos.headline: Scott beats the first-half buzzer with a putback

videos.description: Cane Broome pulls and hits a huge 3-pointer to beat the shot clock late in the second half, giving Cincinnati a 62-58 lead over UConn.
videos.headline: Broome hits deep 3-pointer to beat the shot clock
